---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Ministries">
  <section class="container-x py-12 md:py-20">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Desktop unchanged (md:5xl); mobile comfy -->
      <h1 class="mt-1 md:mt-2 text-3xl md:text-5xl font-medium">
        Life at The Life Place
      </h1>

      <!-- Slogan -->
      <p class="mt-5 md:mt-6 text-base sm:text-2xl text-center text-gray-700">
        Come. See. <span class="text-[#B3282D]">Jesus</span>
      </p>

      <!-- Intro -->
      <p class="mt-4 text-base md:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-7 md:leading-8">
        Our ministries are designed to help people grow in Jesus, build strong families,
        and live out their faith in every sphere of life.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Ministries grid -->
    <div class="mt-8 md:mt-10 grid gap-6 md:gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 md:p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium mb-2">Sunday Gatherings</h3>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 leading-6 md:leading-7">
          Word, worship, prayer, and community every week.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 md:p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium mb-2">Music, singing &amp; dancing</h3>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 leading-6 md:leading-7">
          We echo heaven’s joy with music, singing, and dancing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 md:p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium mb-2">The Lord’s Table</h3>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 leading-6 md:leading-7">
          We gather at the Table to remember what Jesus did for us.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 md:p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium mb-2">See Jesus in the Bible</h3>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 leading-6 md:leading-7">
          Clear, gospel-rich teaching from the Bible.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 md:p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium mb-2">Extravagant generosity</h3>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 leading-6 md:leading-7">
          Made rich by what Jesus has done, we are generous and share in all things.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 md:p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium mb-2">Go live the story</h3>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 leading-6 md:leading-7">
          We are sent out to live the story of Jesus aloud in our city, nation, and the world.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Kids Ministry (Coming Soon) -->
      <div class="rounded-xl border bg-white p-5 md:p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-orange-200">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center sm:items-start justify-between gap-2 mb-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium">Kids Ministry</h3>
          <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-orange-500 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white">
            Coming Soon
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 leading-6 md:leading-7">
          We don’t yet have a children’s ministry. As Jesus provides people and resources, we will begin one where our children too will
          <em> Come. See. Jesus.</em>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scripture footer -->
    <div class="border-t mt-12 md:mt-16 pt-8 md:pt-10 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <blockquote class="text-lg md:text-xl italic text-gray-800">
        “I came that they may have and enjoy life and have it in abundance (to the full, till it overflows)”
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-warmray-600">John 10:10 AMP</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
